{"tid":1702281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11.11 唔係三罷，係開花","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:38:25.000Z","uid":234195,"like":127,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"9763552d8f5253c158c54e7618c315548ff1bfe1","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"如果我有錯，可唔可以屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先，我係非常支持三罷，但，罷一日有咩用？罷一日嘅效用真係唔大，而且大部分打工仔唔會為罷一日工而冒險，導致每次罷工越黎少人參與，越黎越少人信罷工。<br />\n罷工真係唔係話罷就可以罷，既然有人籌備緊工會，點解唔等埋先，黎場真嘅大三罷，咁先可以持續幾個月甚至無限期，令政府跪，你罷一日工政府鬼會理，仲要可能無埋份工，超高風險極低回報。宜家咁臨時臨急罷一日有咩用？唔好話搞完可以再搞，每次搞d人都要估下到底有無人罷，都要諗一次會唔會比人炒，一定一次少過一次，咁點解唔一鋪過，做好曬準備先？<br />\n<br />\n同意平日開花，但可唔可以唔好濫用罷工呢個詞，會令下次真係罷工嘅可信性更低。"},{"pid":"f819ef3cd99edb778170acbe46c11c446ce8903b","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88eebb8164ff02ad16184e1ab2e074356180d139","tid":1702281,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"凌晨荃灣"},{"pid":"0bf11ca1307be06287927bb5b883e4bcdcb25314","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"83f787f3b41088333f81b3fb357ed03dac72e665","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"0c969e75e720cd45f56cc05ced56e54e21656dd1","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"54c725ccbdb4d207db6f343f8e1f84277d0eda4a","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:10:18.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"363868bb5c6ea68d95a5e27d22affb33807901ee","tid":1702281,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"de90559fe32aab6d9327d0c6eae